profile:
Island Pro Bins is a dumpster rental and waste management company based out of North Saanich, BC and serving all of Southern Vancouver Island including Greater Victoria and the Saanich Peninsula.
 
If you have a small-to-medium sized demolition, construction, renovation or clean-up project we have a selection of dumpster bin rentals that will be perfect for your needs.
 
Using newer equipment and professional drivers you can count on your bin to be delivered on-time, picked up when you ask and for a fair and competitive rate.
 
Dumpster rental services include delivery and pick-up of 10 yard rock box/concrete dumpsters, 12 yard standard roll-off dumpsters and 20 yard dumpsters.  We rent dumpsters and waste containers to landscaping contractors, construction contractors, roofers, homeowners, estate clean ups, commercial clean ups and anyone who needs a large, centralized waste container on-site for their project.
 
10 Yard Rock Box Dumpsters:  Our 10 yard rock box dumpsters are perfect for concrete driveway tear outs, concrete pad removals, concrete slab removals, concrete waste, concrete rubble, rock, sand, gravel, aggregates and more.  If it's a heavy material than our 10 yard dumpsters are easy to load with their low-sides and because of their compact size you won't overload them (with too much weight).
 
12 Yard Dump Body Dumpster Rental:  Our 12 yard dump body dumpster is perfect for the removal or delivery of landscaping materials and equipment such as bobcats, skid-steers and mini-excavators.
 
12 Yard Roll Off Dumpster Rentals:  Our 12 yard dumpster rentals are perfect for landscape clean ups, property clean ups, small demolition projects, construction projects, roof tear-offs and more.  A 12 yard dumpster is the equivalent of about 3-4 full-size pickup truck loads.
 
20 Yard Dumpster Rentals:  Our 20 yard dumpster rentals are perfect for medium sized construction, demolition, renovation and clean-up projects.  They are the equivalent of about 6-8 full-size pickup truck loads depending on the materials being loaded.
 
Dumpster Rentals Weight Calculators:  We have some handy weight calculators on our website so you can calculate the rough weight of your materials including drywall, asphalt, concrete and roofing materials.
 
Vacuum Truck Services:  We have a 1500 gallon vacuum truck service for pumping out septic tanks and RV and boat holding tanks.
 
Waste We Accept In Our Dumpster Rentals:
 
Clean Wood Waste
Dirty Wood Waste
Construction Debris (drywall AFTER 1990 with paperwork!)
Concrete, Brick, Cement, Asphalt
Gravel, Sand, Rock, Sod, Dirt
Junk and Garbage.
 
We DO NOT accept any hazardous materials such as paints, chemicals, fuels, fuel canisters, any liquids, pesticides, cleaning agents or any other hazardous material that may require special considerations, restrictions or licensing to haul.
 
Island Pro Bins Provides Dumpster Rental Services In:  Victoria, Oak Bay, Cordova Bay, Esquimalt, View Royal, Colwood, Langford, Saanich, Central Saanich, North Saanich and Sidney.
